<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grievance Management System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h2><b>Grievance Management System</b></h2>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Streamline Your Workplace Grievance Process</h2>
            <p>Secure, Efficient, and Transparent Grievance Handling for Your Organization</p>
            <a href="/login" class="btn">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Features</h2>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>User Management</h3>
                <p>Manage user roles and credentials with secure authentication.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Grievance Submission</h3>
                <p>Submit grievances with detailed information and attachments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Status Tracking</h3>
                <p>Track the status of your grievance with real-time updates and notifications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Department Management</h3>
                <p>Assign grievances to specific departments for efficient handling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>Comments and Feedback</h3>
                <p>Provide comments and feedback on grievances to facilitate resolution.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>We are dedicated to providing a comprehensive solution for managing workplace grievances. Our system ensures that all grievances are handled in a secure, efficient, and transparent manner.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions or need further information, please reach out to us.</p>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>

                <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Grievance Management System. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
